 	CORELDRAW:
	===========
	IN 1989 FIRST INTRODUCED BY COREL CORPORATION.
	 Michel Bouillon and Pat Beirne.


	USE: DRAWING PURPOSE
	EG:
		- logo creation
		- marriage invitation                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 
		- visiting card
		- monthly calendar
		- poster
		- notice
		- sticker (number plate,photo insert)
		-textile design
	how to open corel draw?
		- start --> run --> coreldrw
		or
		-start --> all programs -->
		        -->coreldraw graphics suite x3
		      --> corel draw x3
	extension:
		.cdr	
	parts of coreldraw:
	==============		
		title bar
		menu
		menu items
		tools
		ruler
		property bar
		working area	
		status bar
		transformation (alt+f7)
		     -->position
		      -->rotation 
		      -->scale & mirror
		      --> size
		      --> skew
	tools:
	====
	1) pick tool:
		move              (first click)
		-size alteration (second click)
			rotation
			skew
	2) shape tool (f10)
		- shape tool	 --> shape change
			eg:
			polygon to star
			polygon tool --> sun tv logo

  		step 1: draw polygon with 12 sides
		step 2: click shape tool
		step 3: size alter with mouse
		step 4: add node click in property bar
		step 5: size alter with mosue
		- smudge tool
			--> elastic type
		-roughen brush
			--> zig zag
		- free transform	
			--> 45 degree rotation
			--> 90 degree rotation
			........	
	3) crop tool:

	-  only take selected part of shape using double click.

	knife tool
	=======
		it is used to cut the shape in two ways.
	way 1: stright line
	way2 : pencil type
		note: convert single shape into more shape.
	eraser tool:
	========
		it is used to erase the shape in two ways
	-st.line
	-pencil type (press)
		note: do not divide more parts of shape.
	virtual segment delete:
	=================
		it is used to delete particular parts in single 	shape.
	eg: meet starting and ending point to other shape.
	
	eg: flower draw:
	============
	1) circle draw
	2) alt + f7(transformation)  - position (right side)
			       - select all
			       - rotation ( 90 degree)
	3) smart fill tool : color fill ( use f11 - multicolor)
	4)		      - rotation 45 degree
	5) ctrl + a --> ctrl + g
	6) file --> export -->jpg format -->save ,ok.

					

	zoom tool:
	=======
                    normal click: zoom in	
	using shift key + click : zoom out
	hand tool:
	=======
		moving
	free hand tool:
	==========
    --> drawing purpose same as pencil(press mouse)
    --> draw st. line(step 1: mouse click one point
	           step 2: do not press mouse move next point 
                              step 3: color fill.
		click)

	bezier tool:
	=======
		--> line bend (curve)
		---> use polygon st.line
		step 1: mouse click any position
		step 2: click another position do not release 		mouse with drag.
		step 3: color
		
	artist media tool:
	===========
		--> ready made design
	
	pen tool:
	======
		--> st.line (polygon) + bend line

	polyline tool:
	=========
		--> multiline + pencil combine
		(with continous press mouse)
		
	3 ponit curve tool:
	=============
		line bend  with single line only draw

	interactive connection tool:
	===================
		 steps
	dimension tool:
	===========
		measure 
	smart fill tool:
	==========
		it is used to fill color single or multi with outline.
		
		use f11 --> multi color. (fountain fill)

	smart drawing tool:
	==============
		same as pencil but advanced 

	rectangle tool:
	===========
		lenght x breath
	3 point rectangle tool
	==============
	step 1: first draw line
	step 2: move mouse without press
	
	ellipse tool
	========
		circle,ellipse
	3 point ellipse tool:
	==============
		same as 3 point rectangle
	polygon tool:
	=========
		multi line join more sides
	star tool:
	======
		same as polygon tools
		use shape tool

	complext star tool:
	===============
		joined 3 triagnle
		use shape tool to extra modifiction
	graph paper tool:
	============
		collections of rows & column 
	spiral tool:
	=======
		continous circle with joined one.
		or spring
	step 1:
		draw spiral tool
	step 2:
		pick tool click 
	step 3: hair line --> none
	step 4: text menu --> fit text to path click.
	step 5: type text with your size and color

	Basic shapes:
	=========

	dr.symbol, heart symbol,etc,....
	
	arrow shapes:
	==========
		arrow
		use to : way
	flowchart shapes:
	============
		use programming language shapes
		eg:(input,output,loop,.....)
	banner shapes:
	==========
		readymade design
	callout shapes:
	===========
		story writter.
	text tool:
	========
		it is used to type the text in various way.

	interactive blend tool:
	===============
	connect two shapes.
	
	interactive contour tool:
	================
		border set 
	
	step 1: rectangle draw
	step 2: interactive contour tool click
	step 3: draw on rectangle
	
	interactive distortion tool:
	==================
		corner side change round shape  with middle point draw.
	
	interactive drop shadow tool:
	====================
	 
	shadow photo or shapes
	
	interactive envelop tool:
	=================

	fold shapes
	
	interactive excrude tool:
	=================
	
	perspective view (first big view at end small view)
	
	interactive transparancy tool:
	====================
	color value decrease or increase.

	eye dropper tool:
	===========
		color select 
	eg: face color take accurately

	paint bucket tool:
	===========
		color fill
	outline pen dialog tool:
	================
		hair line (outline )
		use --> color,style,size
	outline color dialog tool:
	=================
		outline color only change
	
	no outline:
	========
		outline hide
	hairline outline:
	==========
		outline show
	color docker window:
	===============
	color fill (cmyk,rgb format) using eye dropper.

	color fill dialog
	===========
		color fill inside shape (no outline)

	fountain fill dialog:
	=============
		multi color (f11)

	pattern fill dialog:
	=============
		ready made pattern
	
	texture fill dialog:
	=============
		ready made pattern
	post script texture:
	============
		ready made pattern	
	no fill:
	=====
		clear ready made pattern
	color docker window:
	===============
		cmyk -- format color.

	interactive fill tool:
	=============
		ready made pattern size change,rotation.

	interactive mess fill tool:
	================
		wrap model ( 9 box ) after drag the readymade pattern

	Shortcut keys:
	===========
	
	full screen/normal screen : f9
	tranformation: alt+f7
	zoom out: f3
	zoom in: f4
	screen size fit: shift+f4
	group: ctrl + g
	ungroup: ctrl + u
	break aprt: ctrl + k
	middle position: p
	pick tool: space
	multicolor : f11
	all select:	ctrl+a 
	symbol: ctrl+ f11
  	back : ctrl+end
  	front: contrl+ home
  	duplicate : ctrl + d
	outline size & color: f12
	export : ctrl + e (to save image format .jpg)
	import : ctrl + i ( to place image)
	visual basic (calender) : alt + f11
	shape format : f10
	
	



	
		
		

	
		
	
	
	

	
		
		

	
		
		
	

	
		

	
			
			
	
